📄 [32m Final Result:[0m 
You can view the TV schedule for any channel on ScreenRant by using the channel selector on the schedule page (https://screenrant.com/db/schedule/hbo/). Selecting a channel loads its schedule on the same page, and each channel also has its own dedicated URL that follows the pattern:

```
https://screenrant.com/db/schedule/<channel-slug>/
```

Replace `<channel-slug>` with the channel’s name in lowercase (and hyphens if needed). For example:
- HBO: https://screenrant.com/db/schedule/hbo/
- ABC: https://screenrant.com/db/schedule/abc/
- CBS: https://screenrant.com/db/schedule/cbs/
- NBC: https://screenrant.com/db/schedule/nbc/
- Fox: https://screenrant.com/db/schedule/fox/

